title: Subzero 700TCI Refrigerator/Freezer with Automatic Ice Maker
item_description:
Subzero 700TCI Refrigerator/Freezer with Automatic Ice Maker

  • Subzero 700TCI
  • Built-in Bottom-Freezer Refrigerator with Spill-Proof Glass Shelves

  • Star-K Certified and Requires Panels/Handles: With Automatic Ice Maker

They have front panels made from Plyboo which is a Bamboo Veneer but the panels can be removed and changed to match kitchen cabinetry.Â
